Package org.jboss.elemento

Interface Container<E extends Element,B extends TypedBuilder<E,B>>

All Superinterfaces:
IsElement<E>, TypedBuilder<E,B>
All Known Implementing Classes:
HTMLContainerBuilder
public interface Container<E extends Element,B extends TypedBuilder<E,B>> extends TypedBuilder<E,B>, IsElement<E>
Provides methods and default implementations for adding elements. 

TodoRepository repository = new TodoRepository();
TodoElement[] elements = repository.todos().stream()
        .map(TodoElement::new)
        .toArray(TodoElement[]::new);
HTMLUListElement ul = ul()
        .addAll(elements)
        .element();
